  "text": "In order to study the reproducibility of tractograms obtained using our approach, we conducted experiments on the Traced dataset which is used in the ISMRM 2017 tractography challenge. Traced contains 20 dMRI images of the same human subject. Images are collected using 2 scanners (Philips 3T) during 2 different sessions per scanner where 5 separate acquisitions are done in each session. A detailed description of the images as well as the dataset can be accessed through the challenge website (https://my.vanderbilt.edu/ismrmtraced2017/). [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] Traced website* -- For all images, we obtained whole brain tractograms consisting of 1.25 million streamlines. All tractograms are obtained using the same parameters shown in Table 3 .",
